OL,6,F"Two teachers and a teenage pupil were
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital with stab wounds.
OL,8,FTheir injuries are not life-
OL,9,Fthreatening.
OL,11,F"A teenage girl has been arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of attempted murder and
OL,13,Fcurrently remains in police custody.
OL,15,F"A knife has been recovered as
OL,16,Fevidence.
